-PREREQUIRED
	gsl			http://www.gnu.org/software/gsl/

-COMPILATION:
	* scons version >= 1.0.0 http://www.scons.org
		* linux
			scons

		* windows
			scons

	* cmake version >= 2.6	http://www.cmake.org
		* linux:
			mkdir build
			cd build
			cmake ../
			make
		*windows:
			mkdir build
			cd build
			cmake ../
			nmake
